Class Administrator

java.lang.Object
app.tracktune.model.user.User
app.tracktune.model.user.AuthenticatedUser
app.tracktune.model.user.Administrator
public class Administrator extends AuthenticatedUser
Represents an administrator user of the TrackTune system. Inherits from AuthenticatedUser and has all its attributes and behaviors.

Administrator accounts typically have elevated privileges compared to regular users.
